          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ico">☎</span>
            <span><strong>Telefon</strong><a href="tel:053125079944" style="color:var(--lime)">0531 / 250 799 44</a></span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ico">🛵</span>
            <span><strong>Abholung</strong>Online-Bestellung via Lieferando · Mo–So 17–22 Uhr</span>
